        <mxCell id="flow" value="&lt;b&gt;Fluxul principal&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1.&lt;/b&gt; User se logheaz&amp;#259; în UI prin Keycloak (realm &lt;b&gt;rsk&lt;/b&gt;) &amp;rarr; prime&amp;#537;te token JWT.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;2.&lt;/b&gt; UI cheam&amp;#259; API-ul (cu Bearer) prin Kong &amp;rarr; &lt;b&gt;importer-service&lt;/b&gt; (/import).&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;3.&lt;/b&gt; importer public&amp;#259; un eveniment pe topicul Kafka &lt;b&gt;product-topic&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;4.&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;data-service&lt;/b&gt; consum&amp;#259; evenimentul &amp;rarr; salveaz&amp;#259; produsul în MySQL.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;5.&lt;/b&gt; UI cite&amp;#537;te produsele prin Kong &amp;rarr; data-service (REST) &amp;rarr; afi&amp;#537;eaz&amp;#259;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:italic&quot;&gt;Toate serviciile valideaz&amp;#259; JWT-ul la Keycloak; logurile merg în ELK.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
