        <mxCell id="legend" value="&lt;b&gt;Legend&amp;#259;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;🟦 albastru = UI&lt;br&gt;🟧 portocaliu = gateway/edge (Kong, nginx)&lt;br&gt;🟩 verde = microservicii business (Java)&lt;br&gt;🟪 mov = Kafka (event bus)&lt;br&gt;🟨 galben = MySQL (date)&lt;br&gt;🟥 ro&amp;#537;u = Keycloak (auth) / ELK (loguri)&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11px&quot;&gt;— continuu = date · ┄ punctat = auth/loguri&lt;/span&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#666;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
